    <section class="prose">
        <p>
            a horror MUD that runs in your terminal. single-player
            adventure and combat, with a shared multiplayer layer.
        </p>
        <p>
            the surface is dying. the heat took your camp three days
            ago. you walked, alone, until you found a hole in the
            ground. the edge crumbled. you fell for a long time. the
            only way out is down.
        </p>
        <p>
            every player carves into the walls. you read what others
            left at the depths you reach. they will read what you
            leave. below depth forty, things find you in the dark ‚ÄĒ
            combat turns on a timed strike and a read of intent. the
            queen waits at depth two hundred.
